'''布蘭頓·思懷茲'''（{{lang-en|'''Brenton Thwaites'''}}，{{bd|1989年|8月10日|catidx=Stone}}）是一名[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]][[男演員|男演員]]。他最著名的作品是在{{link-en|Fox8|Fox8}}的青少年電視劇《''{{link-en|Slide (TV series)|Slide (TV series)|Slide}}''》（2011年）中出演Luke Gallagher角色和電影《[[記憶傳承人：極樂謊言|記憶傳承人：極樂謊言]]》（2014年）中的Jonas一角。他目前在[[DC_Universe_(串流媒體)|DC Universe]]電視劇《[[悍將聯盟|悍將聯盟]]》中飾演[[迪克·格雷森|迪克·格雷森]]。

==個人經歷==
思懷茲生於[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]][[昆士蘭州|昆士蘭州]]的[[凱恩斯_(昆士蘭州)|凱恩斯]]<ref name="Home away from Home">{{cite news|last=Strudwick|first=Daniel|title=Cairns actor Brenton Thwaites trades Far North for a role in Home and Away|url=http://www.cairns.com.au/article/2011/07/26/175505_local-news.html|accessdate=21 September 2011|work=[[The_Cairns_Post|The Cairns Post]]|publisher=[[News_Limited|News Limited]]|date=27 July 2011|archive-date=2012-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121002070115/http://www.cairns.com.au/article/2011/07/26/175505_local-news.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。畢業於[[昆士蘭科技大學|昆士蘭科技大學]]<ref name="QUTalumni">{{cite news|title=Underbelly coup for QUT acting grads|url=http://www.qut.edu.au/alumni/news-and-events/news-and-events?news-id=36871|accessdate=27 September 2011|publisher=[[Queensland_University_of_Technology|Queensland University of Technology]]|date=18 August 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402042536/http://www.qut.edu.au/alumni/news-and-events/news-and-events?news-id=36871|archive-date=2012-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="BrentonSoaps">{{cite news|url=http://www.couriermail.com.au/ipad/brenton-soaps-up-well-for-role/story-fn6cc53j-1226091034637|title=Brenton soaps up well for role|last=Swanwick|first=Tristan|date=9 July 2011|work=[[The_Courier-Mail|The Courier-Mail]]|publisher=[[Queensland_Newspapers|Queensland Newspapers]]|accessdate=27 September 2011|archive-date=2012-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120926035936/http://www.couriermail.com.au/ipad/brenton-soaps-up-well-for-role/story-fn6cc53j-1226091034637|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2010年畢業之後，隨即演出電影《''Charge Over You''》，作為他大銀幕處女作<ref name="COY1">{{cite web|url=http://chargeoveryou.com/about/the-project|title=The Project|publisher=Charge Over You|accessdate=27 September 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120424225307/http://chargeoveryou.com/about/the-project|archivedate=2012年4月24日}}</ref> 。

